revision.text:
The '''1931–32 Segunda División''' season saw 10 teams participate in the second flight Spanish league. [[Real Betis|Betis]] was promoted to [[La Liga|Primera División]]. [[CE Europa|Catalunya]] was relegated to [[Tercera División]].
