The 2010&ndash;11 [[Surinamese Eerste Klasse]] is a season of second-tier [[association football]] in [[Suriname]].

== Changes from 2009&ndash; 10 ==
* Jai Hanuman and FCS Nacional were relegated from the Hoofdklasse
* Kamal Dewaker and The Brothers were promoted to the Hoofdklasse

