The '''Benin Davis Cup team''' represents [[Benin]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Fédération Beninoise de Lawn Tennis]].
==History== Benin competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1993 Davis Cup|1993]]. Their best result was 6th place in Group III in [[1999 Davis Cup|1999]].
==Current team (2018)==
* [[Alexis Klégou]] * Felix Hounkpevi (amateur player) * Magloire Yakpa (amateur player) * Delmas N'tcha (amateur player)
