{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Loei Province Stadium | image = | location = [[Loei province|Loei]], [[Thailand]] | coordinates = {{coord|17.485806|101.734803|format=dms|type:landmark_scale:3000}} | opened = | owner = | operator = | surface = [[Grass]] | construction_cost = | former_names = | tenants = [[Loei City F.C.]] 2010-2011 | seating_capacity = 3,628 }}
'''Loei Province Stadium''' ({{lang-th|สนามกีฬาจังหวัดเลย หรือ สนามริเวอร์ไซด์}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Loei Province]], [[Thailand]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Loei City F.C.]]. The stadium holds 3,628 people.
