{{infobox basketball club | name = UBSC Raiffeisen Graz | color1 = yellow | color2 = blue | logo = UBSC Raiffeisen Graz logo.png | nickname = | image_size = 200px | leagues = [[Österreichische Basketball Bundesliga|ÖBL]] | founded = {{Start date and age|1977}} | dissolved = <!-- or | folded = --> | history = | arena = Unionhalle Graz |capacity=600 | location = | colors = | current = | sponsor = Raiffeisen | president = | vice-presidents = | manager = | coach = Markus Galle | ownership = | championships = | website = [http://www.ubsc-graz.at ubsc-graz.at] | h_body = 0000FF | h_pattern_b = | h_shorts = 0000FF | h_pattern_s = | a_body = FFFF00 | a_pattern_b = | a_shorts = FFFF00 | a_pattern_s = }} '''UBSC Graz''' is a professional [[basketball]] club based in [[Graz]], [[Austria]] that plays in the [[Österreichische Basketball Bundesliga|ÖBL]]. Due to sponsorship reasons, the team was previously also known as '''Raiffeisen Graz'''.
