{{Infobox national volleyball team |name=Uruguay |gender=women |image=Flag of Uruguay.svg |federation=Federación Uruguaya de Voleibol |website=[http://www.uruvoley.com.uy www.uruvoley.com.uy] {{es icon}} |confederation=CSV |manager= |coach=Rafael Codina |Olympic apps= |pattern_la1=|pattern_b1=|pattern_ra1= | leftarm1=87CEFA|body1=87CEFA|rightarm1=87CEFA|shorts1=000000| |pattern_la2=|pattern_b2=|pattern_ra2= | leftarm2=FF0000|body2=FF0000|rightarm2=FF0000|shorts2=000000| }} {{MedalTableTop}} {{MedalCompetition|[[South American Women's Volleyball Championship|South American Championship]]}} {{MedalSilver| [[1951 in sports|1951]] | Rio de Janeiro}} {{MedalSilver| [[1956 in sports|1956]] | Montevideo}} {{MedalBronze| [[1958 in sports|1958]] | Porto Alegre}} {{MedalBronze| [[1969 in sports|1969]] | Caracas}} {{MedalBronze| [[1971 in sports|1971]] | Montevideo}} {{MedalBronze| [[1973 in sports|1973]] | Bucaramanga}} {{MedalBottom}}
The '''Uruguay women's national volleyball team''' is the national team of [[Uruguay]]. The squad won the silver medal at the inaugural [[South American Women's Volleyball Championship|1951 South American Championship]] in [[Rio de Janeiro, Brazil]]. The dominant forces in women's [[volleyball]] on the [[South America]]n continent however became [[Brazil women's national volleyball team|Brazil]] and [[Peru women's national volleyball team|Peru]].
==Results==
===FIVB tournaments=== * [[1960 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship]] &mdash; 9th place * [[1973 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup]] &mdash; 10th place
===[[Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|Pan-American Cup]]=== *[[2002 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2002]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2003 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2003]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2004 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2004]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2005 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2005]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2006 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2006]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2007 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2007]] &mdash; 11th place *[[2008 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2008]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2009 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2009]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2010 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2010]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2011 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2011]] &mdash; did not participate *[[2012 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup|2012]] &mdash; 12th place
===[[South American Women's Volleyball Championship|South American Championship]]=== * [[2005 Women's South American Volleyball Championship|2005]] &mdash; 5th place * [[2007 Women's South American Volleyball Championship|2007]] &mdash; 4th place * [[2009 Women's South American Volleyball Championship|2009]] &mdash; 5th place * [[2011 Women's South American Volleyball Championship|2011]] &mdash; 5th place
